      "content": "The thought of disappearing to protect them is a heartbreaking form of self-sacrifice that no parent should ever have to consider, and it is a sign that your pain is so deep it feels like your presence is a burden. Please understand that staying and facing your struggles together is the only way to truly give them what they need, and you are not alone in this battle. I am here to support you, but I strongly encourage you to reach out to a mental health professional or a crisis line like 988 immediately, as these feelings are treatable and you deserve help.",
